onal acne is <strong>stubborn, unpredictable, and frustrating</strong>. Whether it's caused by stress, periods, or imbalanced hormones, it often feels like nothing truly works—until now. <strong>Blume’s Clear Skin Kit is specifically designed to fight acne at the source, while being gentle enough for sensitive, breakout-prone skin.</strong> Here’s why it’s the game-changer your skin needs:</p></span></div><picture data-rid="cc9cc39d-74a6-4fde-aa34-9e7f5310fe29" class="r-bdu65k"><img src="https://blume.com/cdn/shop/files/hormonal-acne-kit2_1000x700_crop_right.png?v=1760565129" class="r-axg2tv" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div><div data-rid="17061209-0825-4361-92ab-de71fc1ce469" class="r-b3p4fn"><div data-rid="dbb8edd0-6cae-423f-9b7d-98b1b35c64ec" class="r-w5wc32"><div data-rid="0af89f86-442e-4748-89bd-b861dba55b94" class="r-1lw6c1y alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h3>1. Targets Hormonal Acne at the Root</h3></span></div><div data-rid="493ee68f-082b-42fd-8f2b-cdf4b3ffe1a0" class="r-1sjpaib alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Hormonal breakouts are different from regular acne—they stem from deep within the skin, triggered by hormone fluctuations that throw oil production and inflammation into overdrive. Whether it’s due to puberty, pregnancy, menopause, getting off birth control, stress, or really, anything else, these breakouts tend to be stubborn, cystic, and hard to treat with traditional acne products.</p><br><p>Blume’s plant-powered, highly effective formulas are designed to calm inflammation, regulate oil production, and prevent future breakouts before they even reach the surface. By targeting acne at the root—while it's still forming under the skin—you can stop breakouts before they happen instead of constantly treating them after the fact. With just three easy steps, you’ll be on your way to clear, balanced skin—without the frustration of constant hormonal flare-ups.</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="95c15fdc-882b-48ff-885c-5f6e83d5540a" class="r-133j21z"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/2_dd176fad-2d50-4a84-b48e-68ed6a4e7aea.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/2_dd176fad-2d50-4a84-b48e-68ed6a4e7aea.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/2_dd176fad-2d50-4a84-b48e-68ed6a4e7aea.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/2_dd176fad-2d50-4a84-b48e-68ed6a4e7aea.png?v=1732078664" alt="Side-by-side comparison of skin before and after treatment, showing significant improvement." class="r-ikl5dx" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="4883e451-eeea-4bd0-8951-41b16e04fc62" class="r-1w8lkii"><div data-rid="8c2de239-a972-4c81-9895-fdc762bfe181" class="r-1x0eymx"><div data-rid="7d45643b-643c-469a-bfee-617813d66d5b" class="r-ysbqnv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>2. Won’t Mess with Your Skin Barrier</p></span></div><div data-rid="79d1cb9b-f784-4d12-99ac-c821b0d568d9" class="r-1gv4aeo alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Most acne treatments strip your skin, leading to dryness, irritation, and even more breakouts (we see you, over-the-counter spot treatments). Harsh ingredients like benzoyl peroxide and alcohol-based toners can disrupt your skin’s natural protective barrier, leaving it red, flaky, and vulnerable to bacteria—which ironically makes acne worse in the long run.</p><br><p>Blume takes a gentler, smarter approach. It balances acne-fighting ingredients like Black Cumin Seed Oil and Blue Tansy, to combat hormonal breakouts without over-drying or weakening your skin. This means less irritation, faster healing, and a stronger, healthier skin barrier—so your skin can defend itself against future breakouts instead of constantly feeling inflamed and reactive.</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="36ce6db5-7bf1-478e-a754-87a4649e3de3" class="r-1jvjpvh"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/3_5258d4e4-3a70-49e3-96f6-13af736caed3.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/3_5258d4e4-3a70-49e3-96f6-13af736caed3.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/3_5258d4e4-3a70-49e3-96f6-13af736caed3.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/3_5258d4e4-3a70-49e3-96f6-13af736caed3.png?v=1732078664" alt="Skincare products and accessories on a white bathroom counter." class="r-1cwhw0" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="1b4c864c-1442-4a2d-9314-f7ee5fc53b85" class="r-1ey9gn2"><div data-rid="f0d21b6d-54d4-4355-a8c1-20194d158e28" class="r-1nh2rgh"><div data-rid="5a83bb46-3999-4836-aad1-b40b69f9d531" class="r-6sgf1o alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>3. Balances Oil Without Over-Drying</p></span></div><div data-rid="c3cfb210-8b7d-4764-99a1-a00e715bf72d" class="r-ytw1sh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>One of the biggest struggles with hormonal acne? Oily yet dry skin at the same time. Your hormones signal your skin to produce more oil, but at the same time, many acne treatments strip away moisture—leaving your skin both greasy and dehydrated. This imbalance can actually trigger even more breakouts as your skin overcompensates by producing even more oil to make up for the dryness.</p><br><p>Blume’s formulas are designed to restore balance by regulating excess sebum production while maintaining essential hydration. Instead of harsh, drying ingredients that leave your skin feeling tight and irritated, Blume uses lightweight, non-comedogenic hydrators like aloe and hyaluronic acid to keep your skin nourished without clogging pores. The result? A healthy, balanced complexion that’s never too oily or too dry—just clear, calm, and happy.</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="4c187896-e03b-46fe-8c39-fdf87ae09acb" class="r-ab5qh1"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_07_62767c4f-240f-4bf4-ae9e-149e55717059.png?v=1737143146&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_07_62767c4f-240f-4bf4-ae9e-149e55717059.png?v=1737143146&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_07_62767c4f-240f-4bf4-ae9e-149e55717059.png?v=1737143146&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_07_62767c4f-240f-4bf4-ae9e-149e55717059.png?v=1737143146" alt="Close-up of skincare cream with text about ceramides and amino acids." class="r-lxazq0" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="b43223d6-0777-4d83-bbfc-acadb0b7a5b3" class="r-gnwa92"><div data-rid="5c46dfed-113b-4032-b268-25f1f0e488c9" class="r-5tseha"><div data-rid="11b4f3ba-27f8-43ab-8314-0380b772733a" class="r-1g4ioy2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>4. Loved by Thousands with Hormonal Acne</p></span></div><div data-rid="d21efe00-bec6-4f26-9a4d-defc1198413f" class="r-1gu5bgo alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Don’t just take our word for it—thousands of people struggling with hormonal acne and sensitive skin have seen real transformations with Blume. From painful, deep cystic breakouts to clear, balanced skin, our community speaks for itself. With over 5,000 five-star reviews and a growing family of 500,000+ clear-skin believers, Blume is the go-to routine for those who have tried everything and are finally seeing real, lasting results.</p><p>Joi